    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在突如其来的创业失败与沉重债务中，你一无所有，只能回到故乡，从零开始。 <br>你必须从小工作做起，一天一天努力生存，提升能力，与街坊邻里建立联系，寻找新的机会。 <br>但现实并不温柔。 <br>在催债者的压力与资源有限的困境中，你的每一个选择都将决定未来的走向。 <br>你能否从逆境中重新站起来？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>现在就踏上你的生存与逆袭之路吧！</strong></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/9da19025c4f0ec54c314ce131f273cbe.poster.avif?t=1756000641\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/9da19025c4f0ec54c314ce131f273cbe.webm?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/9da19025c4f0ec54c314ce131f273cbe.mp4?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现实向的生存与经济管理</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/7a6d62730e87908bf11e2141ebdaf0e5.poster.avif?t=1756000641\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/7a6d62730e87908bf11e2141ebdaf0e5.webm?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/7a6d62730e87908bf11e2141ebdaf0e5.mp4?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从打零工开始维持生计，合理规划时间和金钱，一步步迈向更好的生活。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在生活开销和还债压力下，每个决定都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能力成长与技能解锁</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/1794523ee7ddd37215fd4aa49b985e80.poster.avif?t=1756000641\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/1794523ee7ddd37215fd4aa49b985e80.webm?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/1794523ee7ddd37215fd4aa49b985e80.mp4?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过锻炼力量、智力、敏捷、感知等能力，解锁更多工作和互动选项。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可通过小游戏、劳动或学习等方式成长，打造属于你的发展路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NPC互动与关系建立</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/dba3a4463a4b569f90c68269d69e67cd.poster.avif?t=1756000641\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/dba3a4463a4b569f90c68269d69e67cd.webm?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/dba3a4463a4b569f90c68269d69e67cd.mp4?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与故乡的居民建立联系，深入了解他们的故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升亲密度可获得奖励或援助，也可能解锁特殊事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实生活模拟系统</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/dfa1f1bea4a4f535705cc565fdb171d3.poster.avif?t=1756000641\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/dfa1f1bea4a4f535705cc565fdb171d3.webm?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/dfa1f1bea4a4f535705cc565fdb171d3.mp4?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理体力、健康和心理状态，维持生活平衡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过工作、休息或爱好活动恢复状态或获得增益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式小游戏体验</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/4130841466128adc2e3cc48ff5050fe2.poster.avif?t=1756000641\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/4130841466128adc2e3cc48ff5050fe2.webm?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317850/extras/4130841466128adc2e3cc48ff5050fe2.mp4?t=1756000641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在工作任务或事件中参与互动小游戏，获取额外奖励，提升游戏代入感。</p></li></ul>",
